headline: Bloomberg Indices Expands Futures-Based Index Offering with New Eris SOFR Swap Futures Tracker Indices
summary: Bloomberg today announced the launch of the Bloomberg Eris SOFR Swap Futures Tracker Indices, 11 new indices designed to track the performance of holding and rolling Eris SOFR Swap futures across the US dollar interest rate curve.

headline: 2 Reasons CME is Risky and 1 Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Over the past six months, CME Group has been a great trade, beating the S&P 500 by 6.1%. Its stock price has climbed to $303.07, representing a healthy 12.1% increase. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
